<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" pages="5">
  <diagram name="Trang-1" id="SLe2oRT_l7HSzYHhVhJu">
    <mxGraphModel dx="2810" dy="-1476" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml GeofenceTieBreakSequenceVi\ntitle Xử lý khoảng cách bằng nhau giữa 2 POI gần nhau\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Người dùng\&quot; as User\ncontrol \&quot;LocationTrackingService\&quot; as LocationTrackingService\ncontrol \&quot;GeofenceOrchestratorService\&quot; as GeofenceOrchestratorService\ncontrol \&quot;GeofenceEvaluationEngine\&quot; as GeofenceEvaluationEngine\nentity \&quot;GeofenceSpatialIndex\&quot; as GeofenceSpatialIndex\ncontrol \&quot;PlaceCatalogService\&quot; as PlaceCatalogService\n\nUser -&gt; LocationTrackingService : Di chuyển vào vùng gần nhiều POI\nactivate LocationTrackingService\n\nLocationTrackingService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Gửi vị trí hiện tại (OnTrackedLocationUpdated())\nactivate GeofenceOrchestratorService\n\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Đánh giá mẫu vị trí (ProcessLocationSampleAsync())\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceEvaluationEngine : Đánh giá geofence và lấy các POI ứng viên gần vị trí hiện tại (Evaluate() -&gt; GetCandidateDefinitions())\nactivate GeofenceEvaluationEngine\n\nGeofenceEvaluationEngine -&gt; GeofenceSpatialIndex : Lấy các POI ứng viên gần vị trí hiện tại (GetCandidateDefinitions())\nactivate GeofenceSpatialIndex\nGeofenceSpatialIndex --&gt; GeofenceEvaluationEngine : Danh sách POI gần nhau (GetCandidateDefinitions())\ndeactivate GeofenceSpatialIndex\n\nGeofenceEvaluationEngine --&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Danh sách trigger hợp lệ\ndeactivate GeofenceEvaluationEngine\n\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Lọc các trigger được phép xử lý\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Ánh xạ trigger thành candidate POI\n\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Chọn POI tốt nhất (GetBestPOIAsync())\nactivate PlaceCatalogService\nPlaceCatalogService -&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Tính điểm ưu tiên cuối cùng (GetFinalPriority())\nPlaceCatalogService -&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Sắp xếp POI theo điểm giảm dần (GetBestPOI())\nPlaceCatalogService -&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Nếu bằng điểm thì ưu tiên LocationId nhỏ hơn (GetBestPOI())\nPlaceCatalogService --&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : POI tốt nhất\ndeactivate PlaceCatalogService\n\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Tìm trigger tương ứng với POI (ResolveTriggerForPoi())\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Kiểm tra điều kiện chuyển POI (ShouldSwitchToCandidatePoi())\n\nalt Không chọn được POI tốt nhất\n    GeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Chọn trigger dự phòng (GeofenceTriggerSelector.SelectBest())\nelse Chọn được POI tốt nhất\n    GeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Giữ trigger đã chọn\nend\n\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Ghi nhớ POI đang được ưu tiên (RememberActivePriorityPoi())\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Chấp nhận trigger được chọn (RaiseTriggerAccepted())\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; GeofenceOrchestratorService : Xử lý POI được ưu tiên\nGeofenceOrchestratorService -&gt; LocationTrackingService : Trả kết quả POI được ưu tiên\nLocationTrackingService --&gt; User : Hiển thị / phát nội dung POI phù hợp\n\ndeactivate GeofenceOrchestratorService\ndeactivate LocationTrackingService\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="iTmAS2fiOg1AQAyFdCFA-5">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="997" width="2437" x="-300" y="2338" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml LocalAudioQueueGeneralVi\ntitle Nhiều du khách cùng nghe audio - Hàng đợi cục bộ trên từng thiết bị\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor white\n  LifeLineStrategy solid\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Du khách 1\&quot; as Visitor1\nactor \&quot;Du khách 2\&quot; as Visitor2\nactor \&quot;Du khách 3\&quot; as Visitor3\n\nboundary \&quot;Ứng dụng mobile\&quot; as App\ncontrol \&quot;GeofenceOrchestratorService\&quot; as Orchestrator\ncontrol \&quot;PlaceCatalogService\&quot; as Catalog\ncontrol \&quot;PlaybackCoordinatorService\\n(Hàng đợi phát cục bộ)\&quot; as Playback\n\npar Thiết bị 1\n    Visitor1 -&gt; App : Chọn POI / nghe audio\n    activate App\n    App -&gt; Orchestrator : Xử lý POI được ưu tiên (HandleTriggerAsync())\n    activate Orchestrator\n\n    Orchestrator -&gt; Catalog : Lấy dữ liệu audio của POI\n    activate Catalog\n    Catalog --&gt; Orchestrator : Audio khả dụng\n    deactivate Catalog\n\n    alt Đang có phiên phát\n        Orchestrator -&gt; Playback : Thêm vào hàng đợi cục bộ (Enqueue())\n        activate Playback\n        Playback --&gt; Orchestrator : Đã thêm vào hàng đợi\n        deactivate Playback\n    else Chưa có phiên phát\n        Orchestrator -&gt; Playback : Tạo hàng đợi và phát ngay (PlayQueueAsync())\n        activate Playback\n        Playback --&gt; Orchestrator : Bắt đầu phát audio\n        deactivate Playback\n    end\n\n    Orchestrator --&gt; App : Trạng thái phát audio\n    deactivate Orchestrator\n    App --&gt; Visitor1 : Nghe nội dung POI\n    deactivate App\n\nelse Thiết bị 2\n    Visitor2 -&gt; App : Chọn POI / nghe audio\n    activate App\n    App -&gt; Orchestrator : Xử lý nội dung tương tự trên hàng đợi cục bộ\n    activate Orchestrator\n    Orchestrator --&gt; App : Trạng thái phát audio\n    deactivate Orchestrator\n    App --&gt; Visitor2 : Nghe nội dung POI\n    deactivate App\n\nelse Thiết bị 3\n    Visitor3 -&gt; App : Chọn POI / nghe audio\n    activate App\n    App -&gt; Orchestrator : Xử lý nội dung tương tự trên hàng đợi cục bộ\n    activate Orchestrator\n    Orchestrator --&gt; App : Trạng thái phát audio\n    deactivate Orchestrator\n    App --&gt; Visitor3 : Nghe nội dung POI\n    deactivate App\nend\n\nnote over App, Playback\nMỗi thiết bị tự quản lý hàng đợi phát audio riêng.\nKhông có hàng đợi phát audio dùng chung trên server.\nend note\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="iTmAS2fiOg1AQAyFdCFA-10">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="794" width="1236" x="50" y="4130" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml AdminQrSequenceVi\ntitle QR cho POI trên trang Admin Web\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Admin\&quot; as Admin\nboundary \&quot;Giao diện QR\\n(LocationQrManager.razor)\&quot; as QrPage\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;LocationQrController\&quot; as QrController\ncontrol \&quot;LocationQrService\&quot; as QrService\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\n\nAdmin -&gt; QrPage : Mở chức năng QR của POI\nactivate QrPage\n\nQrPage -&gt; ApiClient : Lấy trạng thái QR của địa điểm (GetLocationQrStatusAsync())\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; QrController : Gửi yêu cầu lấy trạng thái QR\nactivate QrController\n\nQrController -&gt; DBContext : Kiểm tra quyền và lấy địa điểm được phép thao tác\nactivate DBContext\nDBContext --&gt; QrController : Thông tin địa điểm + audio mặc định\ndeactivate DBContext\n\nQrController -&gt; QrService : Tạo dữ liệu trạng thái QR (BuildStatus())\nactivate QrService\nQrService --&gt; QrController : Dữ liệu QR\ndeactivate QrService\n\nQrController --&gt; ApiClient : Trả về trạng thái QR (LocationQrStatusDto)\ndeactivate QrController\nApiClient --&gt; QrPage : Hiển thị thông tin QR\ndeactivate ApiClient\n\nopt In / tải QR\n    Admin -&gt; QrPage : Chọn tạo preview hoặc tải QR\n    QrPage -&gt; ApiClient : Tạo file QR (GenerateLocationQrAsync())\n    activate ApiClient\n\n    ApiClient -&gt; QrController : Gửi yêu cầu tạo QR\n    activate QrController\n\n    QrController -&gt; DBContext : Kiểm tra quyền và lấy địa điểm được phép thao tác\n    activate DBContext\n    DBContext --&gt; QrController : Thông tin địa điểm + audio mặc định\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    QrController -&gt; QrService : Tạo file QR (GenerateLocationQrFile())\n    activate QrService\n    QrService --&gt; QrController : Tệp QR\n    deactivate QrService\n\n    QrController --&gt; ApiClient : Trả về file QR\n    deactivate QrController\n    ApiClient --&gt; QrPage : Hiển thị preview / tải file QR\n    deactivate ApiClient\nend\n\ndeactivate QrPage\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="iTmAS2fiOg1AQAyFdCFA-14">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="675" width="1472" x="-68" y="4923" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml MobileQrScanUnifiedVi\ntitle Quét QR trên mobile\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Khách tham quan\&quot; as Visitor\nboundary \&quot;App Smart Tourism\\n(QrScannerPage)\&quot; as AppScanner\ncontrol \&quot;QrDeepLinkService\&quot; as DeepLinkService\nboundary \&quot;Camera / Trình duyệt\&quot; as Browser\ncontrol \&quot;LocationQrController\&quot; as QrController\ncontrol \&quot;LocationQrService\&quot; as QrService\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\n\nactivate Visitor\nVisitor -&gt; Visitor : Quét mã QR trên điện thoại\n\nalt Quét bằng app Smart Tourism\n    Visitor -&gt; AppScanner : Quét mã QR\\n(OnBarcodesDetected())\n    activate AppScanner\n\n    AppScanner -&gt; DeepLinkService : Phân tích nội dung QR\\n(ParseDeepLink())\n    activate DeepLinkService\n\n    DeepLinkService --&gt; AppScanner : Trả về kết quả deep link\\n(DeepLinkResult)\n    deactivate DeepLinkService\n\n    AppScanner -&gt; DeepLinkService : Xử lý deep link\\n(HandleDeepLinkAsync())\n    activate DeepLinkService\n\n    DeepLinkService --&gt; AppScanner : Điều hướng đến POI / mở liên kết ngoài\\n(NavigateToLocationAsync() / OpenExternalUrlAsync())\n    deactivate DeepLinkService\n\n    AppScanner --&gt; Visitor : Mở đúng màn hình POI trong app\n    deactivate AppScanner\n\nelse Quét bằng camera / trình duyệt điện thoại\n    Visitor -&gt; Browser : Mở URL công khai\n    activate Browser\n\n    Browser -&gt; QrController : Mở trang landing của POI\\n(GET /LocationQr/public/location/{id})\n    activate QrController\n\n    QrController -&gt; DBContext : Lấy POI + trạng thái + audio + insights\\n(LoadPublicLocationAsync() / BuildLocationLandingInsightsAsync())\n    activate DBContext\n\n    DBContext --&gt; QrController : Trả về dữ liệu POI\n\n    QrController -&gt; DBContext : Lưu lượt mở landing QR\\n(Add() + SaveChangesAsync())\n\n    DBContext --&gt; QrController : Xác nhận đã lưu telemetry\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    QrController -&gt; QrService : Dựng trang landing của POI\\n(RenderLocationLandingPage())\n    activate QrService\n\n    QrService --&gt; QrController : Trả về HTML landing page\n    deactivate QrService\n\n    QrController --&gt; Browser : Trả về HTML landing page\n    deactivate QrController\n\n    Browser --&gt; Visitor : Hiển thị landing page\n\n    Browser -&gt; Browser : Thử mở deep link vào app\\n(tryOpenDeepLink())\n\n    alt Ứng dụng đã được cài\n        Browser --&gt; Visitor : Mở app vào đúng POI\n    else Chưa cài app / mở app thất bại\n        Browser -&gt; QrController : Mở trang tải ứng dụng\\n(GET /LocationQr/public/download)\n        activate QrController\n\n        QrController -&gt; QrService : Dựng trang tải ứng dụng\\n(RenderDownloadPage())\n        activate QrService\n\n        QrService --&gt; QrController : Trả về HTML download page\n        deactivate QrService\n\n        QrController --&gt; Browser : Trả về trang tải ứng dụng\n        deactivate QrController\n\n        Browser --&gt; Visitor : Hiển thị nút tải app / QR tải APK\n    end\n\n    deactivate Browser\nend\n\ndeactivate Visitor\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="k0PbXVgMCdZMVS44L1eZ-6">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="1093" width="1659" x="-240" y="7670" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml StatisticsOverviewSequenceVi\ntitle Statistics Page \n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Admin\&quot; as Admin\nboundary \&quot;Statistics.razor\&quot; as StatisticsPage\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;StatisticsController\&quot; as StatisticsController\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\nboundary \&quot;admin-ui.js\&quot; as AdminJs\n\nactivate Admin\n\nAdmin -&gt; StatisticsPage : Mo trang Statistics / thay doi bo loc\\n(LoadAsync())\nactivate StatisticsPage\n\nStatisticsPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau lay du lieu thong ke tong hop\\n(GetStatisticsAsync())\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; StatisticsController : Goi API thong ke theo bo loc\\n(GET /Statistics?... )\nactivate StatisticsController\n\nStatisticsController -&gt; DBContext : Lay du lieu theo bo loc\\n(BuildStatisticsOverviewAsync())\nactivate DBContext\n\nDBContext --&gt; StatisticsController : Tra ve du lieu tho\\n(tracking, playback, heatmap, location, route, tour...)\ndeactivate DBContext\n\nStatisticsController -&gt; StatisticsController : Tong hop summary, chart, heatmap,\\nroute history, top POI va average listening\\n(BuildHeatmapPoints() va cac xu ly thong ke khac)\n\nStatisticsController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ve goi du lieu thong ke tong hop\\n(StatisticsOverviewDto)\ndeactivate StatisticsController\n\nApiClient --&gt; StatisticsPage : Tra du lieu overview cho trang\ndeactivate ApiClient\n\nStatisticsPage -&gt; StatisticsPage : Cap nhat summary, chart, report,\\nroute history va selected route\\n(LoadAsync())\n\nStatisticsPage -&gt; StatisticsPage : Tao state cho ban do thong ke\\n(CreateStatisticsMapState())\n\nStatisticsPage -&gt; AdminJs : Khoi tao / dong bo heatmap, route,\\ntour overlay va POI tren ban do\\n(initializeStatisticsMap() / syncStatisticsMap())\nactivate AdminJs\n\nAdminJs -&gt; AdminJs : Chuan hoa heatmap points va render ban do\\n(normalizeStatisticsHeatPoints() / renderStatisticsMap())\n\nAdminJs --&gt; StatisticsPage : Hien thi ban do thong ke da cap nhat\ndeactivate AdminJs\n\nStatisticsPage --&gt; Admin : Hien thi tong quan Statistics\\n(summary, chart, heatmap, route history, top POI, average listening)\n\ndeactivate StatisticsPage\ndeactivate Admin\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="k0PbXVgMCdZMVS44L1eZ-11">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="794" width="1997" x="-220" y="10840" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml DashboardOverviewSequenceVi\ntitle Dashboard\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nboundary \&quot;Dashboard.razor\&quot; as DashboardPage\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;DashboardController\&quot; as DashboardController\ncontrol \&quot;AdminRequestAuthorizationService\&quot; as AuthService\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\n\nactivate DashboardPage\n\nDashboardPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau lay tong quan dashboard\\n(GetDashboardOverviewAsync())\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; DashboardController : Goi API tong quan dashboard\\n(GET /Dashboard/overview)\nactivate DashboardController\n\nDashboardController -&gt; AuthService : Xac thuc quyen xem dashboard\\n(AuthorizeAsync())\nactivate AuthService\n\nAuthService -&gt; DBContext : Kiem tra session, user va quyen\nactivate DBContext\nDBContext --&gt; AuthService : Ket qua xac thuc\ndeactivate DBContext\n\nAuthService --&gt; DashboardController : Duoc phep / Tu choi truy cap\ndeactivate AuthService\n\nalt Khong du quyen hoac session het han\n    DashboardController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ve loi truy cap\\n(401 / 403)\n    deactivate DashboardController\n\n    ApiClient --&gt; DashboardPage : Loi tai dashboard\n    deactivate ApiClient\n\n    DashboardPage -&gt; DashboardPage : Hien thi thong bao loi\nelse Duoc phep truy cap\n    DashboardController -&gt; DBContext : Tong hop so lieu dashboard\\n(BuildOverviewAsync())\n    activate DBContext\n\n    DBContext --&gt; DashboardController : So lieu metrics\n    DashboardController -&gt; DBContext : Lay hoat dong gan day\\n(BuildActivitiesAsync())\n    DBContext --&gt; DashboardController : Du lieu activities\n    DashboardController -&gt; DBContext : Lay focus items\\n(BuildFocusItemsAsync())\n    DBContext --&gt; DashboardController : Du lieu focus items\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    DashboardController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ve tong quan dashboard\\n(DashboardOverviewDto)\n    deactivate DashboardController\n\n    ApiClient --&gt; DashboardPage : Du lieu dashboard\n    deactivate ApiClient\n\n    DashboardPage -&gt; DashboardPage : Hien thi metrics, activities va focus items\nend\n\ndeactivate DashboardPage\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="k0PbXVgMCdZMVS44L1eZ-12">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="798" width="1140" x="-200" y="11650" as="geometry" />
