        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml AdminQrSequenceVi\ntitle QR cho POI tren trang Admin Web\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Admin\&quot; as Admin\nboundary \&quot;Giao dien QR\\n(LocationQrManager.razor)\&quot; as QrPage\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;LocationQrController\&quot; as QrController\ncontrol \&quot;LocationQrService\&quot; as QrService\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\n\nAdmin -&gt; QrPage : Mo chuc nang QR cua POI\nactivate QrPage\n\nQrPage -&gt; ApiClient : Lay trang thai QR cua dia diem (GetLocationQrStatusAsync())\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; QrController : Goi API lay trang thai QR\\nGET LocationQr/location/{locationId}/status\\nXu ly tai controller: GetLocationQrStatus()\nactivate QrController\n\nQrController -&gt; DBContext : Kiem tra quyen va lay dia diem duoc phep thao tac\nactivate DBContext\nDBContext --&gt; QrController : Thong tin dia diem + audio mac dinh\ndeactivate DBContext\n\nQrController -&gt; QrService : Tao du lieu trang thai QR (BuildStatus())\nactivate QrService\nQrService --&gt; QrController : Du lieu QR\ndeactivate QrService\n\nQrController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ve trang thai QR (LocationQrStatusDto)\ndeactivate QrController\nApiClient --&gt; QrPage : Hien thi thong tin QR\ndeactivate ApiClient\n\nopt In / tai QR\n    Admin -&gt; QrPage : Chon tao preview hoac tai QR\n    QrPage -&gt; ApiClient : Tao file QR (GenerateLocationQrAsync())\n    activate ApiClient\n\n    ApiClient -&gt; QrController : Goi API tao QR\\nPOST LocationQr/location/{locationId}/generate\\nXu ly tai controller: GenerateLocationQr()\n    activate QrController\n\n    QrController -&gt; DBContext : Kiem tra quyen va lay dia diem duoc phep thao tac\n    activate DBContext\n    DBContext --&gt; QrController : Thong tin dia diem + audio mac dinh\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    QrController -&gt; QrService : Tao file QR (GenerateLocationQrFile())\n    activate QrService\n    QrService --&gt; QrController : Tep QR\n    deactivate QrService\n\n    QrController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ve file QR\n    deactivate QrController\n    ApiClient --&gt; QrPage : Hien thi preview / tai file QR\n    deactivate ApiClient\nend\n\ndeactivate QrPage\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="K_L3rqjm1iieYHNH3m_L-4">
