nhat giao dien sau khi luu\n    deactivate ApiClient\n\nelse Archive\n    LanguagePage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau archive ngon ngu\\n(DeleteLanguageAsync())\n    activate ApiClient\n\n    ApiClient -&gt; LanguageController : Goi API archive ngon ngu\\n(DELETE /Language/{id})\n    activate LanguageController\n\n    LanguageController -&gt; DBContext : Archive ngon ngu, bo default neu can\\nva dam bao luon co ngon ngu mac dinh\\n(SaveChangesAsync())\n    activate DBContext\n    DBContext --&gt; LanguageController : Archive thanh cong\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    LanguageController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ket qua archive\n    deactivate LanguageController\n    ApiClient --&gt; LanguagePage : Cap nhat giao dien sau archive\n    deactivate ApiClient\nend\n\ndeactivate LanguagePage\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="vAADwkPExonPpisjlmIm-1">
