        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml POISequenceVi\ntitle 5. Dia diem / POI\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nboundary \&quot;POIList.razor\&quot; as POIPage\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;LocationController\&quot; as LocationController\ncontrol \&quot;LocationQrController\&quot; as QrController\ncontrol \&quot;ChangeRequestController\&quot; as ChangeRequestController\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\n\nactivate POIPage\n\nPOIPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau lay danh sach POI\\n(GetLocationsAsync())\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; LocationController : Goi API lay danh sach POI\\n(GET /Location)\nactivate LocationController\n\nLocationController -&gt; DBContext : Lay danh sach POI theo quyen\nactivate DBContext\nDBContext --&gt; LocationController : Danh sach dia diem\ndeactivate DBContext\n\nLocationController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ve du lieu POI\\n(LocationDto[])\ndeactivate LocationController\nApiClient --&gt; POIPage : Hien thi danh sach POI\ndeactivate ApiClient\n\nalt Luu POI\n    POIPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau tao moi / cap nhat POI\\n(CreateLocationAsync() / UpdateLocationAsync())\n    activate ApiClient\n\n    ApiClient -&gt; LocationController : Goi API luu POI\\n(POST /Location / PUT /Location/{id})\n    activate LocationController\n\n    LocationController -&gt; DBContext : Kiem tra du lieu va luu POI,\\nanh va cau hinh lien quan\n    activate DBContext\n    DBContext --&gt; LocationController : Luu thanh cong / Loi du lieu\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    LocationController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ket qua luu\n    deactivate LocationController\n    ApiClient --&gt; POIPage : Cap nhat giao dien\n    deactivate ApiClient\n\nelse Archive\n    POIPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau archive POI\\n(DeleteLocationAsync())\n    activate ApiClient\n\n    ApiClient -&gt; LocationController : Goi API archive POI\\n(DELETE /Location/{id})\n    activate LocationController\n\n    LocationController -&gt; DBContext : Archive dia diem\n    activate DBContext\n    DBContext --&gt; LocationController : Archive thanh cong\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    LocationController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ket qua archive\n    deactivate LocationController\n    ApiClient --&gt; POIPage : Cap nhat giao dien\n    deactivate ApiClient\n\nelse Xem / tao QR\n    POIPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau xem / tao QR\\n(GetLocationQrStatusAsync() / GenerateLocationQrAsync())\n    activate ApiClient\n\n    ApiClient -&gt; QrController : Goi API trang thai QR / tao QR\\n(GET status / POST generate)\n    activate QrController\n\n    QrController -&gt; DBContext : Lay POI va audio mac dinh neu co\n    activate DBContext\n    DBContext --&gt; QrController : Du lieu QR\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    QrController --&gt; ApiClient : QR status / QR file\n    deactivate QrController\n    ApiClient --&gt; POIPage : Hien thi hoac tai QR\n    deactivate ApiClient\n\nelse Gui yeu cau thay doi\n    POIPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau thay doi POI\\n(SubmitLocationChangeRequestAsync())\n    activate ApiClient\n\n    ApiClient -&gt; ChangeRequestController : Goi API tao change request\\n(POST /ChangeRequest/location)\n    activate ChangeRequestController\n\n    ChangeRequestController -&gt; DBContext : Tao change request\n    activate DBContext\n    DBContext --&gt; ChangeRequestController : Tao thanh cong\n    deactivate DBContext\n\n    ChangeRequestController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ket qua yeu cau\n    deactivate ChangeRequestController\n    ApiClient --&gt; POIPage : Gui yeu cau thanh cong\n    deactivate ApiClient\nend\n\ndeactivate POIPage\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="vAADwkPExonPpisjlmIm-2">
