        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml InitialLanguageSelectionSequenceVi\ntitle 1. Chon ngon ngu\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Nguoi dung\&quot; as User\nboundary \&quot;LanguagePage.xaml\&quot; as LanguagePage\ncontrol \&quot;LocalizationService\&quot; as LocalizationService\ncontrol \&quot;AppSettingsService\&quot; as AppSettingsService\nentity \&quot;SQLite/MobileDatabaseService\&quot; as MobileDatabaseService\ncontrol \&quot;Permissions\&quot; as Permissions\nboundary \&quot;AppShell\&quot; as AppShell\n\nactivate User\n\nUser -&gt; LanguagePage : Mo man hinh chon ngon ngu\nactivate LanguagePage\n\nLanguagePage -&gt; AppSettingsService : Doc LanguageCode hien tai\nactivate AppSettingsService\nAppSettingsService --&gt; LanguagePage : LanguageCode / mac dinh\ndeactivate AppSettingsService\n\nLanguagePage -&gt; LocalizationService : Ap dung ngon ngu hien tai\\n(ApplyLanguage())\nactivate LocalizationService\nLocalizationService --&gt; LanguagePage : Cap nhat van ban giao dien\ndeactivate LocalizationService\n\nUser -&gt; LanguagePage : Chon ngon ngu\n\nLanguagePage -&gt; LocalizationService : Ap dung ngon ngu da chon\\n(ApplyLanguage())\nactivate LocalizationService\nLocalizationService --&gt; LanguagePage : Cap nhat text va trang thai chon\ndeactivate LocalizationService\n\nUser -&gt; LanguagePage : Nhan Bat dau\n\nLanguagePage -&gt; AppSettingsService : Luu LanguageCode\\n(SaveAsync())\nactivate AppSettingsService\n\nAppSettingsService -&gt; MobileDatabaseService : Luu app_settings.language\nactivate MobileDatabaseService\nMobileDatabaseService --&gt; AppSettingsService : Da luu thanh cong\ndeactivate MobileDatabaseService\n\nAppSettingsService --&gt; LanguagePage : Luu cai dat thanh cong\ndeactivate AppSettingsService\n\nalt Android\n    LanguagePage -&gt; Permissions : Kiem tra / yeu cau quyen vi tri\n    activate Permissions\n\n    alt Khong cap quyen\n        Permissions --&gt; LanguagePage : Denied\n        LanguagePage --&gt; User : Giu o man hinh chon ngon ngu\n    else Da cap quyen\n        Permissions --&gt; LanguagePage : Granted\n        LanguagePage -&gt; AppShell : Chuyen den tab Dia diem\\n(GoToAsync())\n        activate AppShell\n        AppShell --&gt; User : Mo man hinh Dia diem\n        deactivate AppShell\n    end\n    deactivate Permissions\n\nelse Nen tang khac\n    LanguagePage -&gt; AppShell : Chuyen den tab Dia diem\\n(GoToAsync())\n    activate AppShell\n    AppShell --&gt; User : Mo man hinh Dia diem\n    deactivate AppShell\nend\n\ndeactivate LanguagePage\ndeactivate User\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="PuR3pW1kyNaqQgFaz-QU-1">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="886" width="1200" x="20" y="20" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml ViewPoiListMobileSequenceVi\ntitle 2. View POI List\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Nguoi dung\&quot; as User\nboundary \&quot;POI List Screen\&quot; as PoiListScreen\ncontrol \&quot;PlacesViewModel\&quot; as PlacesViewModel\ncontrol \&quot;PlaceCatalogService\&quot; as PlaceCatalogService\ncontrol \&quot;Public Catalog API\&quot; as PublicCatalogApi\nentity \&quot;SQLite/Local Cache\&quot; as LocalCache\nentity \&quot;Server Database\&quot; as ServerDatabase\n\nactivate User\n\nUser -&gt; PoiListScreen : Mo tab Dia diem\nactivate PoiListScreen\n\nPoiListScreen -&gt; PlacesViewModel : Tai catalog POI\\n(LoadCatalogAsync())\nactivate PlacesViewModel\n\nPlacesViewModel -&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Lay catalog\\n(GetCatalogAsync())\nactivate PlaceCatalogService\n\nalt Doc cache / offline data\n    PlaceCatalogService -&gt; LocalCache : Doc catalog da luu\n    activate LocalCache\n    LocalCache --&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Categories + Locations + AudioTracks\n    deactivate LocalCache\n\nelse Sync tu server va cap nhat cache\n    PlaceCatalogService -&gt; PublicCatalogApi : Goi public catalog\\n(GET /Location/public/catalog)\n    activate PublicCatalogApi\n\n    PublicCatalogApi -&gt; ServerDatabase : Lay du lieu catalog cong khai\n    activate ServerDatabase\n    ServerDatabase --&gt; PublicCatalogApi : Categories + Locations + AudioTracks\n    deactivate ServerDatabase\n\n    PublicCatalogApi --&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Public catalog snapshot\n    deactivate PublicCatalogApi\n\n    PlaceCatalogService -&gt; LocalCache : Luu catalog vao cache\n    activate LocalCache\n    LocalCache --&gt; PlaceCatalogService : Da luu thanh cong\n    deactivate LocalCache\nend\n\nPlaceCatalogService --&gt; PlacesViewModel : Catalog snapshot\ndeactivate PlaceCatalogService\n\nPlacesViewModel -&gt; PlacesViewModel : Chuan hoa du lieu POI,\\nap dung bo loc va tao danh sach hien thi\n\nPlacesViewModel --&gt; PoiListScreen : Danh sach POI da loc\ndeactivate PlacesViewModel\n\nPoiListScreen --&gt; User : Hien thi danh sach dia diem\n\ndeactivate PoiListScreen\ndeactivate User\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="PuR3pW1kyNaqQgFaz-QU-2">
