        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml ViewHistoryMobileSequenceVi\ntitle 6. View History\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Nguoi dung\&quot; as User\nboundary \&quot;History Screen\&quot; as HistoryScreen\ncontrol \&quot;HistoryService\&quot; as HistoryService\nentity \&quot;SQLite/Playback History\&quot; as PlaybackHistory\n\nactivate User\n\nUser -&gt; HistoryScreen : Mo man hinh History\nactivate HistoryScreen\n\nHistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryService : Tai lich su da nghe\\n(InitializeAsync())\nactivate HistoryService\n\nHistoryService -&gt; PlaybackHistory : Doc lich su da luu\nactivate PlaybackHistory\nPlaybackHistory --&gt; HistoryService : Danh sach lich su nghe\ndeactivate PlaybackHistory\n\nHistoryService --&gt; HistoryScreen : History items\ndeactivate HistoryService\n\nHistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryScreen : Tinh tong so dia diem\\nva thoi luong lich su\n\nHistoryScreen --&gt; User : Hien thi danh sach lich su\n\nalt Xem chi tiet muc lich su\n    User -&gt; HistoryScreen : Chon mot muc lich su\n\n    HistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryScreen : Mo khung chi tiet,\\nhien thi thong tin va audio track\n\n    alt Co audio track da luu\n        HistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryScreen : Hien thi danh sach audio da nghe\n    else Chua co audio track chi tiet\n        HistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryScreen : Dung danh sach audio mau de hien thi\n    end\n\n    HistoryScreen --&gt; User : Hien thi chi tiet lich su\n\nelse Xoa mot muc lich su\n    User -&gt; HistoryScreen : Chon xoa mot muc\n\n    HistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryService : Xoa muc lich su\\n(RemoveFromHistory())\n    activate HistoryService\n\n    HistoryService -&gt; PlaybackHistory : Xoa muc lich su da luu\n    activate PlaybackHistory\n    PlaybackHistory --&gt; HistoryService : Da xoa thanh cong\n    deactivate PlaybackHistory\n\n    HistoryService --&gt; HistoryScreen : Cap nhat danh sach lich su\n    deactivate HistoryService\n\n    HistoryScreen --&gt; User : Cap nhat danh sach lich su\n\nelse Xoa toan bo lich su\n    User -&gt; HistoryScreen : Chon xoa toan bo lich su\n\n    HistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryScreen : Hien thi xac nhan xoa\n\n    alt Dong y xoa\n        HistoryScreen -&gt; HistoryService : Xoa toan bo lich su\\n(ClearHistory())\n        activate HistoryService\n\n        HistoryService -&gt; PlaybackHistory : Xoa toan bo lich su da luu\n        activate PlaybackHistory\n        PlaybackHistory --&gt; HistoryService : Da xoa thanh cong\n        deactivate PlaybackHistory\n\n        HistoryService --&gt; HistoryScreen : Danh sach lich su rong\n        deactivate HistoryService\n\n        HistoryScreen --&gt; User : Cap nhat danh sach rong\n    else Huy\n        HistoryScreen --&gt; User : Giu nguyen danh sach lich su\n    end\nend\n\ndeactivate HistoryScreen\ndeactivate User\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="WX9SQTEdD-ieiS3XrT58-2">
